originalText.text: Im a business executive and I came across Divine Luxury while searching for a luxury car service to impress new clients of mine. I must say the service was OUTSTANDING! Every detail was taken care of. They were prompt, efficient, with such special attention to detail. It was a Luxury experience the whole way through. The accommodations were meticulous and luxurious indeed. I was contacted to confirm all the details of my reservation ahead of time. Divine Luxury was reliable and treated my clients with the highest level of professional. They did not disappoint. Great to have such a dependable service. This will be my new Go- To for luxury transportation!

originalText.text: Used this car service three times. The first two experiences were great but today I was sent a smelly mini van. First of all, he was late. Secondly, his vehicle smelled so bad i almost threw up. I had to hold my hand over my mouth and nose, the whole ride. I almost missed my appointment because of the smelly gray mini van driver’s tardiness. Please inspect your vehicles before you send them to pick people up!!! Some people are very sensitive to smells and we can’t take vehicles smelling like sewers. Please do better !!
